After the functional tests are finished kick off the Groovy script to Active Scan URLs found by ZAP. 

BOnus:
override false positives:  https://github.com/zaproxy/zap-extensions/wiki/HelpAddonsAlertFiltersAlertFilter
This add-on creates a new endpoint which is accessible through ZAPs REST API. Thus it can be used through scripting to set false positives before a scan starts! 

For more info: https://www.securify.nl/blog/SFY20161101/handling_false_positives_in_automated_security_testing.html

